articles.title: Australia: Missing German backpacker found alive - dw.com
articles.description: The young backpacker went missing over 10 days ago. Police have confirmed her identity, Australian media has reported.
articles.content:
A German backpacker who went missing in western Australia almost two weeks ago has been found alive, Australian media reported on Friday.
